+# Data Model ‚Äî Responsive Layout Refresh
+
+## Article (existing `PostInfo`)
+- **Fields**
+  - `title: string` ‚Äî localized title surfaced in list cards and detail header.
+  - `summary: string` ‚Äî teaser paragraph; optional AI summary on detail page.
+  - `tags: string[]` ‚Äî small taxonomy badges; max 6 shown per card.
+  - `time: string` ‚Äî ISO publish timestamp used for chronological sort.
+  - `date: string` ‚Äî display-friendly date fallback when `time` is absent.
+  - `readingTime: { minutes: number; words: number }` ‚Äî reading aid displayed in header and sidebar.
+  - `filename: string` ‚Äî MDX slug for edit links.
+  - `url: string` ‚Äî Remix route path (e.g. `/blogs/prompt`).
+  - `toc: TocItem[]` ‚Äî heading outline powering table of contents widgets.
+  - `status?: "WIP" | "ready"` ‚Äî filters unfinished drafts from list view.
+  - `author?: string` ‚Äî surface-level attribution.
+  - `content: string` ‚Äî compiled MDX body (rendered in detail view).
+- **Relationships**
+  - Referenced by `BlogListPage` to render cards.
+  - Referenced by `ArticleDetailPage` for hero metadata and MDX body.
+- **Validation Rules**
+  - `title`, `summary`, `url` must be non-empty.
+  - `time` or `date` must parse to a valid `Date`; skip cards that fail.
+  - `readingTime.minutes` clamps to ‚â•1 before display.
+  - `toc.level` constrained to heading depth 2‚Äì4 to fit sidebar spacing.
+
+## BlogListLayout
+- **Fields**
+  - `breakpoints: { mobile: 320-767; tablet: 768-1023; desktop: ‚â•1024 }`.
+  - `columns: { mobile: 1; tablet: 1; desktop: 2 }` ‚Äî optional 3rd column flagged off for this release.
+  - `cardSpacing: { vertical: --space-stack-md; horizontal: --space-inline-md }`.
+  - `cardPadding: { mobile: --space-inset-sm; desktop: --space-inset-md }`.
+  - `aboveFoldTarget: 4` ‚Äî minimum cards visible at 360‚ÄØpx viewport height.
+  - `animation: { duration: 120ms; easing: var(--ease-standard); reduceMotionFallback: 'none' }`.
+- **Relationships**
+  - Consumes `Article` data to seed cards.
+  - Shares token definitions with `PageContainer` primitive in `app/core/ui`.
+- **Validation Rules**
+  - Ensure horizontal overflow is hidden at all breakpoints.
+  - `aboveFoldTarget` verified via automated snapshot test that simulates 360‚ÄØpx viewport.
+  - Hover/focus states must keep accessible contrast (‚â•4.5:1).
+
+## ArticleDetailLayout
+- **Fields**
+  - `readingMeasure: clamp(56ch, 70ch, 80ch)` ‚Äî controls line length across breakpoints.
+  - `verticalRhythm: { headingSpacing: --space-stack-lg; paragraphSpacing: --space-stack-md; mediaSpacing: --space-stack-lg }`.
+  - `sidebar: { width: 18rem; stickyOffset: 112px; maxHeight: calc(100vh - 7rem) }`.
+  - `tocCollapseBreakpoint: 1280px` ‚Äî mobile Drawer vs. desktop sidebar.
+  - `heroSpacing: { title: --space-stack-md; metadata: --space-stack-sm }`.
+  - `scrollRestoration: true` ‚Äî uses Remix `ScrollRestoration` component.
+- **Relationships**
+  - Renders `Article` metadata plus MDX content through `MDXWrapper`.
+  - Shares spacing tokens with BlogListLayout for consistency.
+- **Validation Rules**
+  - Running text must produce 60‚Äì90 characters per line in automated tests.
+  - Sidebar TOC scroll area must retain keyboard focus order.
+  - Media blocks keep caption and image within the same spacing stack.
+
+## LayoutTokenSet
+- **Fields**
+  - `--space-stack-sm|md|lg`: numeric rem values for vertical rhythm.
+  - `--space-inline-sm|md`: horizontal padding scale.
+  - `--font-size-body`, `--line-height-body`, `--font-size-heading-lg`: typography scale updates.
+  - `--ease-standard`, `--transition-fast`: animation variables capped at 150‚ÄØms.
+- **Relationships**
+  - Injected into `:root` via `app/styles/tailwind.css`, consumed through Tailwind utilities (`[--space-stack-md]`, custom classes).
+  - Referenced by both layout components and MDX wrappers.
+- **Validation Rules**
+  - Tokens must meet WCAG contrast in both light/dark themes.
+  - Documented in `quickstart.md` with guidance for reuse.
+  - Modifications require updating Tailwind safelist if custom properties used in arbitrary values.
